org.apache.paimon.data

Interface InternalArray

  • All Superinterfaces:
    DataGetters
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    BinaryArray, ColumnarArray, GenericArray, HivePaimonArray, SafeBinaryArray

    @Public
public interface InternalArray
extends DataGetters
    Base interface of an internal data structure representing data of ArrayType.

    Note: All elements of this data structure must be internal data structures and must be of the same type. See InternalRow for more information about internal data structures.

    Since:
    0.4.0
    See Also:
    GenericArray
